snippet.title: Rift of the NecroDancer – Launch Trailer – Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Rift of the NecroDancer is available now on Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/en-ca/store/products/rift-of-the-necrodancer-switch/?utm_source=SW&utm_medium=soytnoa&utm_campaign=A1013-01&utm_id=A1013-01

The NecroDancer's back in an all-new rhythm game! Dragged into a strange new world, Cadence must engage in musical combat with monsters surging through the Rift!

#NintendoSwitch #NintendoDirect #RiftoftheNecrodancer

Visit Nintendo.com for more info: https://www.nintendo.com/us/
